    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nitrogen Narcosis is a thalassophobes deep diving nightmare, set in sinking and sunk abandoned facilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and up to 7 other employees wearing the cheapest deep-dive suit money can buy are sent in to recover old materials from these facilities and return it to your captains submarine!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the descent into madness as you slowly slip into a state of hallucinations from nitrogen narcosis symptoms, all while trying to survive against whatever creatures or mutations lurk inside the facility.<br><br>Now, explore the Arctic Circle with the Arctic Freeze Update, which adds a new location, a new creature, and a host of exciting new loot!&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is INVITE ONLY and does not currently feature a server browser, this means to play with others you will have to invite them or be invited to a lobby via Steam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creatures: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore the facilities you will run across a sweep of creatures, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ranging from </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >sharks who snuck their way in, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/ef96cbe9f0ab21a6af653b53ee696f55.poster.avif?t=1734392324\" width=616 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/ef96cbe9f0ab21a6af653b53ee696f55.webm?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/ef96cbe9f0ab21a6af653b53ee696f55.mp4?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >crabs who love to horde loot, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/623aafef8f5b6b8b06728f0d09e7c020.poster.avif?t=1734392324\" width=616 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/623aafef8f5b6b8b06728f0d09e7c020.webm?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/623aafef8f5b6b8b06728f0d09e7c020.mp4?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >all the way to mutant horrors like specimen 2626, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/a38ccd8ec2e3166cd6e21498d9a40581.poster.avif?t=1734392324\" width=616 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/a38ccd8ec2e3166cd6e21498d9a40581.webm?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/a38ccd8ec2e3166cd6e21498d9a40581.mp4?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Facilities: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The facilities you explore play a vital role in your experience, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From entering at the Shallows where the waters surface is still visible and the facilities isn't even flooding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/9422d384541b21eb988c8bcfae2ad60a.poster.avif?t=1734392324\" width=616 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/9422d384541b21eb988c8bcfae2ad60a.webm?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/9422d384541b21eb988c8bcfae2ad60a.mp4?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the way to the Deep where light is rare, facilities are large, and dangers are everywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/c7d61bb1c39b8f48fc67143e0aaa6faa.poster.avif?t=1734392324\" width=616 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/c7d61bb1c39b8f48fc67143e0aaa6faa.webm?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051960/extras/c7d61bb1c39b8f48fc67143e0aaa6faa.mp4?t=1734392324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each facility has a special layout that is different with each play sessions, Facilities also contain Key-card based doors, automatic doors, secondary airlocks, and even doors that might be a little to dangerous to open.</p>",
